g.text: Shows a list of freelancers and asks the collaborator to pick one
Shows the chosen freelancer and asks for confirmation.
shows the list of tasks associated with the chosen freelancer and asks the Collaborator to pick one.
Shows the task and asks for confirmation.
Asks for the details about the execution of the task (end date, delay, brief description of the quality of the work).
Shows the data and asks for confirmation
Confirms and the system calculates the amount to pay.
Shows the amount to pay to the freelancer, then informs the Collaborator of the success of the operation.
